Third Department,

July, 1983

(July 21, 1983)* In the Matter of David R. Singiser, as Assigned Counsel for Edward Turner, Jr., Petitioner, v M. Andrew Dwyer, Jr., as County Judge of Rensselaer County, et al., Respondents.

Not published with other decisions of July 21, 1983, 96 AD2d 644. [Rep.

Application, pursuant to CPLR article 78, for judgment in the nature of mandamus, denied, and petition dated June 20,1983, dismissed on the ground that this proceeding does not lie (CPLR 7801). Mahoney, P. J., Mikoll, Yesawich, Jr., Weiss and Levine, JJ., concur.
